*-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Basic usage examples
*-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* RF classification: numeric (but discrete) y variable
sysuse auto, clear
pyforest_dev foreign trunk mpg price, type(classify) 

* RF classification: string y variable
sysuse auto, clear
gen foreign_str = "Foreign"
replace foreign_str = "Domestic" if foreign==0
pyforest_dev foreign_str trunk mpg price, type(classify) 

* RF regression: continuous y variable
sysuse auto, clear
pyforest_dev price mpg foreign trunk, type(regress) 

* RF regression: use mae rather than mse as node splitting criterion
sysuse auto, clear
pyforest_dev price mpg foreign trunk, type(regress) criterion(mae)

